{"tid":2343731,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"10名港人深圳受審　外國領事館代表未獲入法院聽審","createTime":"2020-12-28T07:02:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-28T07:05:05.000Z","uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4dd02d15c218528cf3e3b80629a9e4d4e7b65c87","tid":2343731,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T07:02:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1567454-20201228.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1567454-20201228.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=%2BrTTj2V4oNsvrkryR3gjd2vf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=6ccf54fc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1567454-20201228.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=f0c47116\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1567454-20201228.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"53e0fdaecd4bbedc91ae5a6f3d51705c69540b33","tid":2343731,"uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T07:03:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1567454-20201228.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1567454-20201228.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=%2BrTTj2V4oNsvrkryR3gjd2vf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=6ccf54fc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1567454-20201228.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=f0c47116\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1567454-20201228.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n12名涉嫌偷渡被扣押在深圳的港人，其中10人的案件下午2時半在深圳鹽田法院開審。<br />\n<br />\n數名外國領事館代表，包括美、英、加拿大、葡萄牙、澳洲及荷蘭的代表，中午約一時半抵達法院門口外，希望入內聽審，但直至原訂開審時間，他們仍未獲准進入法院。<br />\n<br />\n本台與其他記者在法院外拍攝期間，有便衣公安檢查記者證，並表示在疫情期間不要聚集，盡快離去。<br />\n<br />\n12名港人的家屬昨日發公開信，表示12名港人中，有英國、葡萄牙和越南公民，家屬擔心案件會變成「秘密審訊」，促請各國政府派使館人員到庭旁聽，確保審訊公平公正。"},{"pid":"16ff4c73176a98391ad031639f226de0d06013c0","tid":2343731,"uid":36178,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T07:04:15.000Z","msg":"美、英、加拿大、葡萄牙、澳洲及荷蘭的代表<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf65b7e8ba811285562ed74591124227fbd6d8e1","tid":2343731,"uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T07:04:46.000Z","msg":"數名外國領事館代表，包括美、英、加拿大、葡萄牙、澳洲及荷蘭的代表，中午約一時半抵達法院門口外，希望入內聽審，但直至原訂開審時間，他們仍未獲准進入法院。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇黎呢單案西方國家都好緊張，五眼只欠紐西蘭，歐盟有兩個國家做代表"},{"pid":"c8317b1c89752e5b25bf77bdc223c2f33cc5efb3","tid":2343731,"uid":77277,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"16ff4c73176a98391ad031639f226de0d06013c0","tid":2343731,"uid":36178,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T07:04:15.000Z","msg":"美、英、加拿大、葡萄牙、澳洲及荷蘭的代表<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T07:05:05.000Z","msg":"向英吉利開戰！<br />\n向美利堅開戰！"}]}